@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tpdgvc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(0.28)
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.75)) * ((v2 + 0.97 * tmp + 0.06) - v2))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.40)))
    v1 = wp.cos((0.30 / (tmp + 0.87 * v2 + 0.54)))
    v0 = 0.30
    tmp = wp.abs(0.07)
    v0 = v1
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v1 + 0.54) / (v1 + 0.12 / tmp + 0.53)))
    data[tid] = v0
